{"tid":1896091,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"MRNA 武漢疫苗炒作區","createTime":"2020-02-25T02:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T17:14:44.000Z","uid":113074,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9c8a7af74cc099b918a94a752f3fb04b44a9076c","tid":1896091,"uid":113074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T02:33:16.000Z","msg":"好消息！比預想的都快！<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》剛剛報道，美國製藥公司Moderna，已經成功研製出針對新冠病毒肺炎&mdash;&mdash;SARS-CoV-2的人體疫苗，並已將第一批疫苗送美國國家衞生研究院開啟安全性臨牀試驗。<br />\n<br />\nwm<br />\n<br />\n之前，該公司主導該疫苗的科學家還稱，相關疫苗研發可能需要3個月以上&mdash;&mdash;在本次疫情全球科研通力攻堅的基礎上。<br />\n<br />\n但現在，用時1個月，他們就完成了振奮人心的大進展。<br />\n<br />\n美國公司宣佈研製出新冠肺炎疫苗<br />\n<br />\nModerna，美國知名的生物製藥公司，由哈佛團隊創辦於2010年，初名&ldquo;ModeRNA&rdquo;。"},{"pid":"b0d641bb66c91c82f6dd17fdb1cc2eaaaee03560","tid":1896091,"uid":33540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T02:36:20.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"670e38cba44e70f8f95310404e8dade106bf37cf","tid":1896091,"uid":38570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T02:39:36.000Z","msg":"咁咪同GILD爭飯食"},{"pid":"a4ca5715af6f7c25ae6eb912620c5a1b75912bdb","tid":1896091,"uid":149096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"670e38cba44e70f8f95310404e8dade106bf37cf","tid":1896091,"uid":38570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T02:39:36.000Z","msg":"咁咪同GILD爭飯食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T02:40:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f193f1a966e6ddac3936945ab6950537996ca171","tid":1896091,"uid":113074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"670e38cba44e70f8f95310404e8dade106bf37cf","tid":1896091,"uid":38570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T02:39:36.000Z","msg":"咁咪同GILD爭飯食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T02:41:46.000Z","msg":"一個疫苗<br />\n一個減傷<br />\n<br />\n唔同性質"},{"pid":"d72599f638ae358026a606d95232a3e2df1d4bf3","tid":1896091,"uid":38416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"